load ../owned-harness-compaction.maude

--- Coverage: compaction elides an old entry to a reference.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-COMPACTION :
  compacting oldEntry
  =>* C:Cfg elided .

--- Bite: a recent-window entry is never elided by compaction. The RESIDUAL soup
--- var means an elided in any reachable state is a solution, so No solution
--- proves the recent window survives compaction.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-COMPACTION :
  compacting recentEntry
  =>* elided RESIDUAL:Cfg .
